  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Existing law, the California Community Care Facilities Act, provides for the licensing and regulation of community care facilities, as defined, by the State Department of Social Services.\n\nThis bill would make technical, nonsubstantive changes to a provision relating to the California Community Care Facilities Act."
    }
